	<div class="commentBody">	
		<div id="comment_body_2113842">We were surprised at Wolf3D mods, but we knew it was going to happen with DOOM.  I worked with some of the Wolf3D map editor guys before DOOM was even released, but they didn't wind up making the popular level editors.
<br>
<br>The editor and utility source code was released quite early, but it was all for NeXT workstations in Objective-C, so it had to wait for someone to rewrite it for more conventional systems.
<br>
<br>John Carmack
<br></div>
	</div>

